Package com.mygdx.game.entity

Contains classes relating to characters in the game overworld.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Character
    Represents a character in the overworld.
    Character.CharacterComparator
    Compares characters according to their y coordinate.
    NPC
    Represents a non-player character in the overworld.
    Player
    Represents the player character in the overworld.
    RoboNPC
    Represents the robot boss of the game.
    SallyNPC
    Represents the shop keeper NPC.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Character.CharacterState
    Represents the state of a character.
    Character.Direction
    Represents the direction that a character is facing.
